---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Fluid Typography">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-200 text-sm mb-8 inline-block">‚Üê Back to demos</a>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">Fluid Typography</h1>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-12">
        clamp() + viewport vs container. Resize the right box to see container-based scaling.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900 p-6">
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Media / viewport</div>
          <h2 class="fluid-mq font-semibold text-zinc-100">
            Heading scales with viewport
          </h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-2">
            Resize browser window to see change. clamp(1.25rem, 2vw + 1rem, 3rem)
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="resize-x overflow-auto min-w-[280px] max-w-xl rounded-xl border border-emerald-900/50 bg-emerald-950/20 p-6"
        >
          <div class="text-xs font-mono text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
            Container query
          </div>
          <div class="fluid-cq-wrapper">
            <h2 class="fluid-cq font-semibold text-zinc-100">
              Scales with container
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-2">
            Drag right edge. clamp(1.25rem, 8cqi + 0.5rem, 2.5rem)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-8">
        <code class="bg-zinc-800 px-1 rounded">cqi</code> = 1% of container inline size. Same heading in a sidebar vs hero =
        appropriate size.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <style>
    .fluid-mq {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2vw + 1rem, 3rem);
    }

    .fluid-cq-wrapper {
      container-type: inline-size;
      container-name: fluid;
    }

    .fluid-cq {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 8cqi + 0.5rem, 2.5rem);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
